      right: ["Tetany and carpopedal spasm from hypocalcemia", "Cardiac arrhythmias from hypokalemia (U waves, flattened T waves)", "Peripheral edema and ascites from hypoalbuminemia", "Altered mental status from severe metabolic derangement"]
